<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 03:41:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>AH-64阿帕奇被伊朗击落，美国将进行报复：特朗普（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-shot-down-by-iran-u-s-will-retaliate-trump</link><description>&lt;p&gt;AH-64 坠入阿曼湾，机组人员被无人船救起，现在特朗普称这是由于敌人的行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-shot-down-by-iran-u-s-will-retaliate-trump"&gt;伊朗击落 AH-64 阿帕奇后，美国将进行报复：特朗普（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 22:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-shot-down-by-iran-u-s-will-retaliate-trump</guid></item><item><title>这是将被击落的阿帕奇船员从阿曼湾救出的海盗船无人机船</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/this-is-the-corsair-drone-boat-that-plucked-the-downed-apache-crew-out-of-the-gulf-of-oman</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国海军在中东的顶级无人机特遣部队今年三月才开始操作海盗船无人水面舰艇。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/this-is-the-corsair-drone-boat-that-plucked-the-downed-apache-crew-out-of-the-gulf-of-oman"&gt;“这是从阿曼湾救出被击落的阿帕奇船员的海盗船无人机船”&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 19:40:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/this-is-the-corsair-drone-boat-that-plucked-the-downed-apache-crew-out-of-the-gulf-of-oman</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰人工智能无人机攻击俄罗斯后勤系统的内幕</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-ai-enabled-drone-campaign-targeting-russian-logistics-deep-behind-the-lines</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一名负责“中程”无人机行动的军官对无人机对俄罗斯后勤中心的打击提供了前所未有的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-ai-enabled-drone-campaign-targeting-russian-logistics-deep-behind-the-lines"&gt;乌克兰人工智能无人机行动深入后方，瞄准俄罗斯后勤保障的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 19:30:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-ai-enabled-drone-campaign-targeting-russian-logistics-deep-behind-the-lines</guid></item><item><title>Ravenstorm 是空中客车公司全新战斗无人机产品组合的核心</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ravenstorm-at-the-center-of-airbuss-new-combat-drone-portfolio</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着欧洲下一代旗舰战斗机的开发，空中客车公司在无人驾驶协作战斗机上投入了大量资金。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ravenstorm-at-the-center-of-airbuss-new-combat-drone-portfolio"&gt;《Ravenstorm At the Center of Airbus&amp;#39;s New Combat Drone Portfolio》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 18:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ravenstorm-at-the-center-of-airbuss-new-combat-drone-portfolio</guid></item><item><title>AH-64 阿帕奇船员在霍尔木兹海峡附近坠落后被无人机船救起（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-crew-rescued-by-drone-boat-after-going-down-near-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这是已知的首次使用无人水面舰艇来营救坠落的机组人员，也是未来发展的重要标志。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-crew-rescued-by-drone-boat-after-going-down-near-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;AH-64 阿帕奇机组人员在霍尔木兹海峡附近坠落后被无人机救起（更新）后&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 13:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-crew-rescued-by-drone-boat-after-going-down-near-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>VC-25B 空军一号“桥梁”飞机现在涂上了特朗普喜欢的红、白、蓝油漆</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job</link><description>&lt;p&gt;VC-25B“桥”喷气式飞机也在今年夏天正式首次亮相之前进行最后一轮改装。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job"&gt;VC-25B 后的空军一号“桥梁”飞机现在涂上了特朗普喜欢的红、白、蓝油漆，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 01:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job</guid></item><item><title>硫磺岛号完成部署，尼米兹返回美国</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/iwo-jima-completes-deployment-nimitz-heading-back-to-the-united-states</link><description>&lt;p&gt;以下是截至 2026 年 6 月 8 日美国航空母舰和大型两栖攻击舰的位置。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/iwo-jima-completes-deployment-nimitz-heading-back-to-the-united-states"&gt;硫磺岛完成部署后，尼米兹返回美国&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 21:21:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/iwo-jima-completes-deployment-nimitz-heading-back-to-the-united-states</guid></item><item><title>法德未来战斗机努力因不可调和的分歧而失败</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/franco-german-future-fighter-effort-collapses-over-irreconcilable-differences</link><description>&lt;p&gt;德国和法国未能就要求达成一致，这显然导致了欧洲旗舰下一代战斗机计划的结束。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;后&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/franco-german-future-fighter-effort-collapses-over-irreconcilable-differences"&gt;法德未来战斗机努力因不可调和的分歧而崩溃&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 20:44:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/franco-german-future-fighter-effort-collapses-over-irreconcilable-differences</guid></item><item><title>KC-135 加油机被发现配备新型卫星通信天线</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/kc-135-tanker-sporting-new-large-antenna-points-to-major-communications-upgrade</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国空军表示，改善连接性对于 KC-135 机队的生存能力和有效性至关重要。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/kc-135-tanker-sporting-new-large-antenna-points-to-major-communications-upgrade"&gt;配备新卫星通信天线的 KC-135 加油机&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 19:40:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/kc-135-tanker-sporting-new-large-antenna-points-to-major-communications-upgrade</guid></item><item><title>伊朗和以色列从悬崖边退了一步</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-and-israel-step-back-from-the-brink</link><description>&lt;p&gt;经过一系列针锋相对的打击后，以色列和伊朗退出了另一场全面战争。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-and-israel-step-back-from-the-brink"&gt;伊朗和以色列从悬崖边退后&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 08 Jun 2026 18:06:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/iran-and-israel-step-back-from-the-brink</guid></item></channel></rss>